videos.description: Kansas runs the fast break to perfection with Lagerald Vick leaving the pass for Josh Jackson to throw down a vicious tomahawk dunk that leaves the bench in awe.
videos.headline: KU's Jackson tries to annihilate rim on fast-break dunk
UAB's William Lee with a huge block to prevent a lay-in
After a Devonte' Graham three pointer, UAB's Deion Lavender races down court as time expires to score

videos.description: Kansas' Josh Jackson is filling up his resume with powerful dunks, including this latest offering of a vicious slam right over a UAB defender.
videos.headline: Jackson posterizies defender with ridiculous dunk
